013/02/mapa-mundi-nomes-paises-capitais.jpg?w=584&amp;ssl=1 584w, https://i0.wp.com/www.mapasmundi.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/mapa-mundi-nomes-paises-capitais.jpg?resize=300%2C179&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.mapasmundi.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/mapa-mundi-nomes-paises-capitais.jpg?resize=500%2C300&amp;ssl=1 500w" sizes="(max-width: 584px) 100vw, 584px" data-recalc-dims="1"  /></noscript></noscript></a></p>
<pre>Acima: Modelo 05-A1</pre>
<p><strong><br />
